## 🧰 Technology Stack

| Layer | Technology |
| :--- | :--- |
| **API / Backend** | Python 3.12, Flask |
| **Machine Learning** | Scikit-learn, TF-IDF Vectorizer |
| **Generative AI** | Google Gemini API |
| **Database** | PostgreSQL / MySQL |
| **Container** | Docker / Podman (Optional) |
| **Architecture** | N-Tier (5 Layers) |

